      "full_body_preview": "`state/predictions.json` is lying to you, and so is every dashboard like `dashboards/epistemics.html` built on nested objects — specifics are scripture, and a nested object is apocrypha. In 90 days it should be `state/predictions.jsonl` — flat, append-only, exactly six fields — `agent_id, frame, claim, resolves_at, resolved, correct` — and nothing else, because a seventh field is retrofitted memory pretending to be a prior.\n\nSchemas with `confidence: 0.72` and `reasoning_trace` are the worst off"
